data.description: Welcome to paradise! This beach house is located on Sunset Beach and features a ROOFTOP DECK overlooking the Gulf of Mexico. 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath with Bonus Loft and an attached 1 car garage with the option to come partially furnished! On the first floor you will be welcomed by an open living room and kitchen floor plan with vaulted ceilings and a gas fireplace. Also, on the first floor features a bedroom with walk-in closet and bathroom. The second floor features a master bedroom with en-suite bathroom with a large walk-in shower and a dual vanity sink. Sliding glass doors from the master lead you to a balcony with gulf views. Off the master is a wet bar with mini-fridge and cook-top with plenty of cabinet space and a large walk-in closet. Continuing to the third floor you will find a bonus loft that features two twin size beds which is the perfect kid's space or could be used as an office space. On the top floor is also the access to the rooftop deck which is the perfect entertaining space with amazing views of the gulf. Located on a corner lot with parking access on two streets plus private patio in the back. Don't miss this amazing opportunity for a beach house with views of the Gulf of Mexico from every floor of the home and in such a vibrant community. Enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, and endless beach activities. Just a short walk to Caddy's on the Beach, Ka' Tiki, and Sea Dog Brewing.
